Singapore's%20upscale%3C%2Fa%3E%20ION%20Orchard%20mall%2C%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20city's%20luxury%20shopping%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuilding%20a%20brand%20during%20the%20pandemic%20in%20an%20already%20saturated%20market%20and%20for%20a%20conservative%20audience%20was%20not%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22022cb402-7fe6-4f49-937e-82ce83cfdd37%5C%22%3EPouring%20savings%20and%20severance%20pay%20into%20the%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224653%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cheak's%20store%20in%20Ion%20Orchard%20mall%2C%20Singapore.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6909b40c0be9845f2dc5a513%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223102%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBouquets%20of%20flowers%20greeted%20me%20outside%20Cheak's%20newly%20opened%20store%20in%20ION%20Orchard%2C%20Singapore.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EExercise%20and%20sports%20have%20always%20been%20a%20big%20part%20of%20the%20founders'%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYiong%20was%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-opt-for-team-bonding-workout-classes-over-happy-hour-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EF45%20trainer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20practiced%20yoga%2C%20pilates%2C%20and%20Muay%20Thai%2C%20and%20is%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhyrox-founder-races-separate-normal-people-greek-statues-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etraining%20for%20her%20first%20Hyrox%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Chng%20was%20part%20of%20a%20national%20team%20representing%20Singapore%20at%20the%202011%20Touch%20Rugby%20World%20Cup%20and%20has%20also%20dabbled%20in%20cheerleading%2C%20pilates%2C%20yoga%2C%20and%20HIIT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Chng%20was%20laid%20off%20from%20ClassPass%20in%202020%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20go%20all%20in%20on%20an%20athleisure%20clothing%20line%2C%20which%20started%20off%20with%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BButter.%26quot%3B%20They%20