0need%20padding%3B%20it's%20non-negotiable.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20commonly%20asked%20questions%20we%20get%20is%2C%20'Does%20it%20have%20padding%3F'%26quot%3B%20Chng%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20padding%20changes%20the%20construction%20completely%20for%20the%20product%20%E2%80%94%20it%20requires%20so%20many%20more%20stitches%2C%20and%20it%20makes%20it%20difficult%20to%20have%20a%20very%20clean%20bind%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20issue%20was%20the%20sheerness%20of%20the%20fabric.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOverseas%20brands%20don't%20double%20line%20their%20lighter%20colors%20because%20I%20think%20the%20women%20are%20a%20bit%20more%20comfortable%20with%20a%20slight%20sheerness%2C%20but%20in%20Singapore%2C%20that's%20not%20acceptable%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20when%20you%20double-line%20a%20garment%2C%20it%20becomes%20very%20thick.%20So%2C%20we%20spent%20about%20a%20year%20changing%20the%20fabric%20and%20reducing%20its%20thickness%20so%20that%20when%20we%20double-lined%20it%2C%20it%20would%20still%20be%20comfortable%2C%26quot%3B%20Chng%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDesigning%20clothes%20for%20a%20customer%20base%20that%20likes%20to%20play%20it%20safe%20requires%20a%20good%20deal%20of%20restraint%2C%20the%20founders%20said.%20They%20said%20there%20was%20plenty%20they%20wanted%20to%20experiment%20with%2C%20but%20had%20to%20tone%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20brands%20that%20are%20quite%20popular%20internationally%20are%20quite%20sexy%20and%20crazy%20nowadays%2C%26quot%3B%20Yiong%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20take%20that%20idea%2C%20and%20tweak%20it%20to%20what%20will%20work%20for%20our%20audience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e7be9cd0-6781-4711-aad6-8b04c36729a3%5C%22%3EStanding%20out%20from%20the%20Lululemons%20and%20Alo%20Yogas%20of%20the%20world%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225346%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20clothing%20rack%20in%20Cheak's%20store.%5C%22%20ch