3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFresh%20international%20brands%2C%20let's%20say%20Alo%2C%20for%20example%2C%20they%20come%20in%20bringing%20winter%20season%20clothes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20winter%3B%20we%20only%20have%20one%20season%2C%20so%20the%20fabric%20needs%20to%20be%20cooling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheak's%20prices%20are%20slightly%20lower%20than%20those%20of%20its%20foreign%20competitors.%20One%20of%20Cheak's%20bestselling%20sports%20bras%20costs%2055%20Singapore%20dollars%2C%20or%20about%20%2442%2C%20while%20a%20similar-looking%20piece%20from%20Lululemon%20costs%20S%2458.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227349ee06-e1fc-4030-9498-9da0e383cabf%5C%22%3EMaintaining%20a%20friendship%20while%20running%20a%20business%20together%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225413%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yiong%20and%20Chng%20in%20front%20of%20their%20new%20store%20in%20ION%20Orchard.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690b031f0be9845f2dc5bed8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223609%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYiong%20and%20Chng%20have%20rules%20for%20maintaining%20their%20friendship%20while%20remaining%20business%20partners.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20business%20has%20yet%20to%20come%20between%20the%20founders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOutside%20of%20work%2C%20we%20don't%20talk%20about%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Chng%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20see%20each%20other%20on%20weekends%2C%20and%20our%20partners%20hang%20out%20together%2C%20but%20we%20never%20talk%20about%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20flipside%2C%20at%20work%2C%20they%20don't%20talk%20about%20other%20things%2C%20helping%20to%20distinguish%20their%20%26quot%3Bwork%20personality%20and%20friend%20personality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYiong%20handles%20the%20backend%20work%2C%20while%20Chng%20handles%20the%20creative%20and%20customer-facing%20parts%20of%20the%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20work%