20sitting%20on%20her%20couch%2C%20using%20a%20laptop%2C%20in%20her%20new%20Naples%20apartment.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F693c58e4832e0ef1ead625e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221094%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3Ecaptiontk%3Cp%3EKaitlyn%20Rosati%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAdmittedly%2C%20I%20spent%20my%20first%20four%20days%20in%20Italy%20inside%20my%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realized%20I%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fburnout%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erecovering%20from%20burnout%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20beyond%20that%2C%20spending%20time%20somewhere%20long-term%20added%20a%20layer%20of%20anxiety%20I%20didn't%20expect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20the%20thought%20of%20trying%20to%20go%20outside%20and%20speak%20another%20language%20felt%20debilitating.%20I%20was%20initially%20afraid%20I%20would%20sound%20stupid%20if%20I%20couldn't%20find%20the%20right%20words%20in%20Italian%2C%20but%20now%20that%20I've%20been%20here%20for%20nearly%20two%20months%2C%20I've%20forced%20myself%20not%20to%20revert%20to%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20still%20have%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go%2C%20I've%20made%20plenty%20of%20leaps%20language-wise%20%E2%80%94%20I%20even%20purchased%20a%20new%20pair%20of%20glasses%2C%20entirely%20in%20Italian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20also%20experienced%20new%20lifestyle%20shifts%20and%20quirks.%20For%20instance%2C%20I'm%20still%20adjusting%20to%20Italy's%20recycling%20system%3A%20Here%2C%20you%20separate%20paper%2C%20glass%2C%20plastic%2C%20food%20waste%2C%20and%20nonorganic%20items%20into%20separate%20bins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20sounds%20simple%20enough%2C%20but%20the%20system%20is%20a%20lot%20harder%20to%20navigate%20when%20you're%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20dispose%20of%20a%20cotton%20swab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShopping%20for%20food%20and%20household%20items%20looks%20different%2C%20too.%20In%20Naples%2C%20I%20often%20have%20to%20go%20to%20different%20stores%20to%20buy%20produce%2C%20meat%2C%20cheese%2C%20and%20toiletries%2C%20whereas%20I%20could%20have%20found%20all%20these%20items%20at%20one%20supermarket%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20change%20I've%20come%20to%20embrace%2C%20though%3A%20I've%20even%20befriended%20my%20local%20butcher%2C%20Angelo%2C%20who%20makes%20the%20best%20chicken%20cutlets%20I've%20ever%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20groceries%2C%20one%20of%20the%20best%20parts%20of%20living%20here%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-aldi-items-save-money-dietitian-mom-recommendations-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elow%20cost%20of%20food%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I've%20been%20able%20to%20get%20a%20full%20haul%20of%20meat%2C%20cheese%2C%20wine%2C%20water%2C%20and%20produce%20for%2022%20euros%20(or%20about%20%2426).%20This%20same%20array%20of%20items%20would've%20cost%20me%20closer%20to%20%24150%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDining%20out%20is%20also%20much%20more%20affordable%20here.%20One%20night%2C%20I%20took%20myself%20to%20dinner%20and%20got%20a%20personal%20pizza%20and%20a%20glass%20of%20wine%20for%20just%208%20euros.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20New%20York%2C%20it's%20tricky%20to%20find%20a%20nice%20restaurant%20where%20a%20glass%20of%20wine%20costs%20under%20%2420.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2204a83411-f632-4b45-8841-f72c1bbf3621%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENow%2C%20I%20appreciate%20Naples%20even%20more%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20writer%20strolling%20down%20an%20alleyway%20in%20Naples%2C%20Italy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F693c5b72832e0ef1ead62641%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221190%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3Ecaptiontk%3Cp%3EKaitlyn%20Rosati%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20only%20love%20Naples%20for%20its%20affordability%2C%20th