rences%2C%20colours%2C%20themes%2C%20and%20even%20the%20mood%20they%20want%20to%20create.%20Manya%20sketches%20five%20or%20six%20design%20options%2C%20balancing%20length%2C%20floral%20motifs%2C%20and%20detailing%20before%20she%20begins%20crocheting.%20%E2%80%9CI%20undid%20my%20first%20%3Cem%3Evarmala%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethree%20times%20before%20it%20felt%20right%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20pair%20takes%20about%20four%20to%20five%20hours%20to%20craft.%20Basic%20designs%20with%20a%20single%20string%20of%20flowers%20and%20beads%20start%20at%20Rs%203%2C500%2C%20while%20customised%20versions%20can%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%209%2C500%20or%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECouples%20can%20choose%20not%20just%20the%20colours%20and%20flowers%2C%20but%20also%20add%20small%20personal%20details.%20%E2%80%9COne%20couple%20wanted%20their%20college%20colours%20included%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20where%20they%20fell%20in%20love%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20the%20beauty%20of%20crochet%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20not%20just%20saving%20flowers%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20saving%20a%20moment%2C%20a%20story%2C%20a%20piece%20of%20love%20stitched%20by%20hand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F475664%2Fsustainability-mafia-students-climate-startups-climate-solutions-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESustainability%20%3C%2Fa%3Eplays%20a%20role%20here%20too.%20Manya%20prefers%20cotton%20yarn%20for%20its%20lightness%20and%20comfort%2C%20and%20she%20often%20upcycles%20beads%20or%20embellishments%20from%20old%20jewellery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20has%20been%20her%20biggest%20stage.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20by%20posting%20crochet%20work%20online.%20Consistency%2C%20sharing%20behind-the-scenes%2C%20connecting%20with%20people%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20orders%20came%20in.%20Now%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20steady%20stream%20of%20queries%2C%20espec